comment._content: 44-58 Harrington Street, The Rocks. On War Jang & Co., 50-52 Harrington Street. PUBLIC NOTICES, The Sydney Morning Herald, Monday 19 May 1902, p. 2 - The view is looking south. Fence at left overlooks Globe Street. Looking north from the same spot - [http://www.flickr.com/photos/state-records-nsw/4625663728/] This view also shows these terrace houses - [http://www.flickr.com/photos/state-records-nsw/4886823514/] Almost certainly a 1901 Rocks Resumption photographic survey photograph. Google Maps Street View - goo.gl/maps/qkNp2
